------------------------------------------------
-- BUILD
------------------------------------------------

./autogen.sh

If you've installed libevent locally, specify the path to your local
install directory

./configure --with-libevent=$HOME/local

where $HOME/local is the equivalent to /usr/local

------------------------------------------------
-- RUN
------------------------------------------------

If running locally

    ./run.sh [extra args]

If running via ssh

    ssh machine /path/to/ssh-run.sh

For a set of machines

    ./restart-memc.sh

